```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant SPA as SPA (Public Client)
    participant U as User Browser
    participant AS as Authorization Server (PingOne)
    participant PDP as PDP Component (PingAuthorize)
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant MS as Microservice (Wire Transfer)
    participant SAB as SAB Core Banking (Legacy)

    Note over SPA,AS: Phase 1 - Authorization Request with RAR

    SPA->>AS: GET /authorize?response_type=code<br/>&authorization_details=[{type:wire_transfer,<br/>amount:47500, creditorIBAN:FR76...}]<br/>&code_challenge=S256&scope=openid+wire_transfer

    Note over AS: Structural validation only
    Note over AS: authorization_details format valid ?
    Note over AS: type wire_transfer supported ?
    Note over AS: amount is a positive number ?
    Note over AS: IBAN format valid ?
    Note over AS: client_id allowed for this type ?

    AS-->>U: Login page

    Note over SPA,AS: Phase 2 - Authentication and Consent

    U->>AS: Authenticate (credentials)

    Note over AS: User is now identified
    Note over AS: subject is known

    AS->>PDP: Evaluate consent request<br/>{<br/>  subject: user123,<br/>  action: wire_transfer,<br/>  transactionContext: {<br/>    amount: 47500.00,<br/>    currency: EUR,<br/>    creditorIBAN: FR76...,<br/>    debtorIBAN: FR76...<br/>  }<br/>}

    Note over PDP: Enrich from PingOne<br/>(groups, daily_limit)
    Note over PDP: Is the amount within daily limit ?
    Note over PDP: Is the creditor IBAN on a fraud watchlist ?

    PDP-->>AS: decision: allow + consent details

    AS-->>U: Consent screen<br/>"Authorize EUR 47,500.00 to ACME Corp SAS<br/>(FR7630006000011234567890189) ?"

    U->>AS: Confirm

    Note over SPA,AS: Phase 3 - Token Issuance

    AS-->>SPA: 302 redirect ?code=AUTH_CODE

    SPA->>AS: POST /token<br/>(code + code_verifier)

    AS-->>SPA: access_token {<br/>  sub: user123,<br/>  scope: wire_transfer,<br/>  authorization_details: [{<br/>    type: wire_transfer,<br/>    amount: 47500.00,<br/>    creditorIBAN: FR76...,<br/>    debtorIBAN: FR76...<br/>  }]<br/>}

    Note over SPA,SAB: Phase 4 - API Call and Policy Enforcement

    SPA->>GW: POST /transfers<br/>(Bearer token + transaction body)

    Note over GW: Check 1 - JWT signature valid ?
    Note over GW: Check 2 - Token not expired ?
    Note over GW: Check 3 - Audience matches this service ?
    Note over GW: Check 4 - Scope wire_transfer present ?

    GW-->>SPA: 401 if any technical check fails

    GW->>MS: Forward request (token + body)

    Note over MS: Re-validate JWT independently
    Note over MS: RAR Binding - token.amount == body.amount ?
    Note over MS: RAR Binding - token.creditorIBAN == body.creditorIBAN ?
    Note over MS: RAR Binding - token.debtorIBAN == body.debtorIBAN ?

    MS-->>SPA: 403 if RAR binding check fails

    MS->>PDP: POST /v1/data/banking/transfers<br/>{<br/>  subject: user123,<br/>  action: wire_transfer,<br/>  transactionContext: {<br/>    amount: 47500.00,<br/>    currency: EUR,<br/>    creditorIBAN: FR76...,<br/>    debtorIBAN: FR76...<br/>  },<br/>  runtimeContext: {<br/>    already_spent_today: 2000.00,<br/>    transaction_history_count: 3<br/>  }<br/>}

    Note over PDP: Enrich from PingOne<br/>(groups, daily_limit)
    Note over PDP: Policy 1 - Amount within daily limit ?
    Note over PDP: Policy 2 - Creditor IBAN not flagged ?

    PDP-->>MS: decision: allow / deny + reason

    MS-->>SPA: 403 + reason if PDP denies

    MS->>SAB: Initiate transfer (all checks passed)
    Note over SAB: Trusted legacy system
    Note over SAB: Outside OAuth2 perimeter
    Note over SAB: Called via internal service account
    SAB-->>MS: Transfer confirmed
    MS-->>SPA: 200 Transfer initiated
```
